OL,3,CCouncillors approve casino plans for
OL,4,CLondon Trocadero
OL,6,FWestminster Council has approved plans
OL,7,Fto convert the iconic Trocadero
OL,8,Fbuilding in central London into a 24-
OL,9,Fhour casino.
OL,11,FGenting Casinos UK applied to
OL,12,Frepurpose the former Opium nightclub
OL,13,Fin the basement, the ground floor of
OL,14,Fthe souvenir shop, and the former
OL,15,FBubba Gump restaurant on the first
OL,16,Ffloor of the premises at 13 Coventry
OL,17,FStreet.
OL,19,FThe plans would create a two-storey a
OL,20,Fcasino and entertainment venue with
OL,21,Fcapacity for 1,250 customers.
