OL,3,CCouncillors approve casino plans for
OL,4,CLondon Trocadero
OL,6,FCouncillors voted unanimously to
OL,7,Fapprove the proposals, which Genting
OL,8,FUK says will create up to 350 jobs.
OL,10,FThe application received strong
OL,11,Fobjections from the Soho Society,
OL,12,Fwhich argued another "alcohol-led
OL,13,Fgambling venue" in the West End could
OL,14,Flead to more anti-social behaviour.
