OL,3,CCouncillors approve casino plans for
OL,4,CLondon Trocadero
OL,6,FIn their objection, the community
OL,7,Forganisation wrote: "Coventry Street
OL,8,Falready struggles with pedestrian
OL,9,Fcongestion, noise and litter and a new
OL,10,F24-hour casino would actively
OL,11,Fundermine Westminster's 2023
OL,12,FCumulative Impact Assessment (CIA) and
OL,13,Fconflicts with the Soho Neighbourhood
OL,14,FPlan's aims to curb further stress on
OL,15,Fresidential amenity and public realm.
OL,17,F"There is no substantial public
OL,18,Fbenefit offered to outweigh the
OL,19,Fincreased late-night activity,
OL,20,Fspecifically no contribution toward
OL,21,Fpublic toilets."
