OL,3,CCouncillors approve casino plans for
OL,4,CLondon Trocadero
OL,6,FCouncillors argued that casinos
OL,7,F"contribute little to disorder and
OL,8,Fother adverse effects".
OL,10,FThey said: "The main reason for the
OL,11,Flow impact of casinos is that the use
OL,12,Fdoes not attract large groups of high-
OL,13,Fspirited or rowdy persons, and the
OL,14,Fgaming experience is a sober one
OL,15,Fmainly for individuals or small
OL,16,Fgroups."
OL,18,FThe Trocadero is Grade II listed
OL,19,Fbuilding, which has been an
OL,20,Fentertainment venue since the 1850s.
