OL,3,CCouncillors approve casino plans for
OL,4,CLondon Trocadero
OL,6,FIt was modernised in the 1980s,
OL,7,Fhosting facilities such as SegaWorld
OL,8,Ftheme park, Funland and Arcade Area,
OL,9,Fand Cineworld cinema.
OL,11,FThe first floor and basement are
OL,12,Fcurrently vacant.
OL,14,FGenting UK already runs 32 casino
OL,15,Fvenues in the UK - with four in the
OL,16,Fcapital. It has launched a separate
OL,17,Flicensing application for the use of
OL,18,Fthe Trocadero as a casino.
